{"tid":2076793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劉伯溫 - 三峽預言","createTime":"2020-06-23T21:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T00:18:10.000Z","uid":80108,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"090d70c65f38d290ab9d439c00d82afea8bbc689","tid":2076793,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T21:45:03.000Z","msg":"輕氣動山嶽，一線鐵難當。<br />\n<br />\n人逢猛虎難迴避，有福之人住山莊。繁華市，變汪洋。高樓閣，變坭崗。<br />\n<br />\n父母死，難埋葬。爹娘死，兒孫扛。萬物同遭劫，蟲蟻亦遭殃。"},{"pid":"118496f347bccf340f705798f02d04a13616a546","tid":2076793,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:29:38.000Z","msg":"好似好堅咁，ching 世外高人？"},{"pid":"09b1ee0eb838554118b25941319e310989e60282","tid":2076793,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uzMud3Ilyac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuzMud3Ilyac&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Jcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=678bca4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uzMud3Ilyac</a>"}]}